byline.original: By STEVEN ERLANGER and STEPHEN CASTLE

snippet: NATO’s secretary general, Anders Fogh Rasmussen, said Turkey’s tense relations with Cyprus over natural gas exploration and with Israel were “a matter of concern.”
lead_paragraph: NATO’s secretary general, Anders Fogh Rasmussen, said Turkey’s tense relations with Cyprus over natural gas exploration and with Israel were “a matter of concern.”

headline.main: Turkey’s Rifts With 2 Nations Worry a Top NATO Official

headline.seo: NATO Leader Worried by Turkey’s Rifts With Cyprus and Israel
